### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Fase 09 - Testes e Qualidade (Regressivo)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### @name tmf634ResourceSpecificationCreateInvalidBusinessRuleV9
### Deve retornar 422 (estrutura minima de negocio invalida)
POST {{tmfBaseUrl}}/resourceSpecification
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "Spec sem estrutura minima",
	"lifecycleStatus": "Active"
}

### @name tmf634ResourceSpecificationPatchInvalidBusinessRuleV9
### Deve retornar 422 (patch que viola regra minima)
PATCH {{tmfBaseUrl}}/resourceSpecification/{{resourceSpecificationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"resourceCategory": [
		{
			"id": ""
		}
	]
}

### @name tmf634ResourceSpecificationConflictV9
### Deve retornar 409 (conflito de uniqueKey)
PATCH {{tmfBaseUrl}}/resourceSpecification/{{resourceSpecificationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"resourceSpecCharacteristic": [
		{ "name": "Brand", "value": "Huawei" },
		{ "name": "Model", "value": "F670L" },
		{ "name": "categoria", "value": "P" }
	]
}

### @name tmf634ResourceSpecificationListInvalidFieldsV9
### Deve retornar 400 com payload TMF de erro
GET {{tmfBaseUrl}}/resourceSpecification?offset=0&limit=20&fields=id,fieldNaoPermitido
Content-Type: application/json

### @name tmf634ResourceCatalogGetNotFoundV9
### Deve retornar 404 com payload TMF de erro
GET {{tmfBaseUrl}}/resourceCatalog/id-inexistente
Content-Type: application/json

